To install Gordon Service (and all the other tools from the Gordon Suite) you need to use the EOS Gordon Installer.

First of all you need to download the installer:

1. Go to https://eos-solutions.github.io/Gordon/
1. Click on Download
1. When downloaded, open it and click on “Install”
1. After that, the EOS Gordon Installer will automatically open

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000979-0/GordonInstall.png"><br>

**Gordon Service must be installed machine-wide**
With the EOS Gordon Installer, the Gordon Service can be installed as follow: 
1. Open the EOS Gordon Installer as Administrator
2. Click on the setting button in the top right corner
3. Change the scope to **"machine-wide"** and close the setting page
4. go to the “Not Installed” tab, find **Gordon Service** and click on Install.